# This directory holds source research documents that ground the harness design.
# Initial population happens via scripts/pre-flight.sh which moves the three
# documents (Claude_Architecture, SAGE harness analysis, NIST SP 800-218) from
# the repo root into this directory.
#
# Files in this directory are treated as read-only source material. Do not edit
# them. To supersede a research reference, update foundation/04-research-references.md
# and cite the new source.
